draft}} {{ill|1842|ja|1842nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 12|ja|11月12日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Ōyama Gen|ja|大山厳|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , Marshal of the Army (died {{ill|1916|ja|1916th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
