{{Lunisolar October}} '''October 10''' is the 10th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=Kannazuki|1=Kannazuki|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Eiroku|ja|永禄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 10th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1567|ja|1567th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 10|ja|11月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – In the {{ill|Todai-ji Daibutsuden Battle|ja|東大寺大仏殿の戦い|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , due to a surprise attack by {{ill|Matsunaga Hisahide|ja|松永久秀|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the {{ill|Todai-ji Daibutsuden|ja|東大寺大仏殿|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} burned down. * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1577|ja|1577th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 19|ja|11月19日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – In the {{ill|Shigisan Castle Battle|ja|信貴山城の戦い|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Matsunaga Hisahide|ja|松永久秀|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} shattered the famed weapon {{ill|Kotenyō Heipingumo|ja|古天明平蜘蛛|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and subsequently committed suicide. * {{ill|Kanei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1629|ja|1629th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 24|ja|11月24日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – Fuku, the wet nurse of {{ill|Tokugawa Iemitsu|ja|徳川家光|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , entered the palace and received the title of {{ill|Kasuga no Tsubone|ja|春日局|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Births == * {{ill|Genpō|ja|元豊 (宋)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1082|ja|1082nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Huizong|ja|徽宗|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 8th emperor of the {{ill|Northern Song|ja|北宋|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died {{ill|1135|ja|1135th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kenpo|ja|建保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1218|ja|1218th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 30|ja|10月30日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Chūkō|ja|仲恭天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 85th {{ill|Emperor|ja|天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died {{ill|1234|ja|1234th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1830|ja|1830th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 24|ja|11月24日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Seikawa Hachirō|ja|清河八郎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , founder of the Mibu rōshitai (the precursor to the {{ill|Shinsengumi|ja|新選組|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) (died {{ill|1863|ja|1863rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Dōkō|ja|道光|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 15th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1835|ja|1835th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 29|ja|11月29日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Empress Dowager Cixi|ja|慈禧太后|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Western Empress Dowager), consort of {{ill|Emperor Xianfeng|ja|咸豊帝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and a de facto dictator of the late {{ill|Qing Dynasty|ja|清|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died {{ill|1908|ja|1908th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 13th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1842|ja|1842nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 12|ja|11月12日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Ōyama Gen|ja|大山厳|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , Marshal of the Army (died {{ill|1916|ja|1916th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
