2=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 21|ja|11月21日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Yamamoto Tsuna|ja|山本常朝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a {{ill|samurai|ja|Samurai|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born {{ill|1659|ja|1659th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Enkyō|ja|Enkyō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1747|ja|1747th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 12|ja|11月12日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Shimazu Yoshitaka|ja|島津吉貴|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 4th lord of the {{ill|Satsuma Domain|ja|薩摩藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born {{ill|1675|ja|1675th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
