{{Lunisolar October}} '''October 10''' is the 10th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki}} the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Eiroku|ja|永禄}} 10th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|1567|ja|1567th year}} {{ill|November 10|ja|11月10日}} ) – In the {{ill|Todai-ji Daibutsuden Battle|ja|東大寺大仏殿の戦い}} , due to a surprise attack by {{ill|Matsunaga Hisahide|ja|松永久秀}} , the {{ill|Todai-ji Daibutsuden|ja|東大寺大仏殿}} burned down. * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era}} 5th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|1577|ja|1577th year}} {{ill|November 19|ja|11月19日}} ) – In the {{ill|Shigisan Castle Battle|ja|信貴山城の戦い}} , {{ill|Matsunaga Hisahide|ja|松永久秀}} shattered the famed weapon {{ill|Kotenyō Heipingumo|ja|古天明平蜘蛛}} and subsequently committed suicide. * {{ill|Kanei|ja|寛永}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1629|ja|1629th year}} {{ill|November 24|ja|11月24日}} ) – Fuku, the wet nurse of {{ill|Tokugawa Iemitsu|ja|徳川家光}} , entered the palace and received the title of {{ill|Kasuga no Tsubone|ja|春日局}} .
