== Events == * {{ill|Eiroku|ja|永禄}} 10th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|1567|ja|1567th year}} {{ill|November 10|ja|11月10日}} ) – In the {{ill|Todai-ji Daibutsuden Battle|ja|東大寺大仏殿の戦い}} , due to a surprise attack by {{ill|Matsunaga Hisahide|ja|松永久秀}} , the {{ill|Todai-ji Daibutsuden|ja|東大寺大仏殿}} burned down. * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era}} 5th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|1577|ja|1577th year}} {{ill|November 19|ja|11月19日}} ) – In the {{ill|Shigisan Castle Battle|ja|信貴山城の戦い}} , {{ill|Matsunaga Hisahide|ja|松永久秀}} shattered the famed weapon {{ill|Kotenyō Heipingumo|ja|古天明平蜘蛛}} and subsequently committed suicide. * {{ill|Kanei|ja|寛永}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1629|ja|1629th year}} {{ill|November 24|ja|11月24日}} ) – Fuku, the wet nurse of {{ill|Tokugawa Iemitsu|ja|徳川家光}} , entered the palace and received the title of {{ill|Kasuga no Tsubone|ja|春日局}} .
== Births == * {{ill|Genpō|ja|元豊 (宋)}} 5th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|1082|ja|1082nd year}} {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日}} ) – {{ill|Huizong|ja|徽宗}} , the 8th emperor of the {{ill|Northern Song|ja|北宋}} (died {{ill|1135|ja|1135th year}} ). * {{ill|Kenpo|ja|建保}} 6th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|1218|ja|1218th year}} {{ill|October 30|ja|10月30日}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Chūkō|ja|仲恭天皇}} , the 85th {{ill|Emperor|ja|天皇}} (died {{ill|1234|ja|1234th year}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1830|ja|1830th year}} {{ill|November 24|ja|11月24日}} ) – {{ill|Seikawa Hachirō|ja|清河八郎}} , founder of the Mibu rōshitai (the precursor to the {{ill|Shinsengumi|ja|新選組}} ) (died {{ill|1863|ja|1863rd year}} ). * {{ill|Dōkō|ja|道光}} 15th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1835|ja|1835th year}} {{ill|November 29|ja|11月29日}} ) – {{ill|Empress Dowager Cixi|ja|慈禧太后}} (Western Empress Dowager), consort of {{ill|Emperor Xianfeng|ja|咸豊帝}} and a de facto dictator of the late {{ill|Qing Dynasty|ja|清}} (died {{ill|1908|ja|1908th year}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保}} 13th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1842|ja|1842nd year}} {{ill|November 12|ja|11月12日}} ) – {{ill|Ōyama Gen|ja|大山厳}} , Marshal of the Army (died {{ill|1916|ja|1916th year}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Hakuchi|ja|白雉}} 5th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|654|ja|654th year}} {{ill|November 24|ja|11月24日}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Kōtoku|ja|孝徳天皇}} , the 36th Emperor. * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1577|ja|1577th year}} {{ill|November 19|ja|11月19日}} ) – {{ill|Matsunaga Hisahide|ja|松永久秀}} , a {{ill|samurai|ja|Samurai}} (born {{ill|1510|ja|1510th year}} ). * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1707|ja|1707th year}} {{ill|November 3|ja|11月3日}} ) – {{ill|Utsunomiya Tonan|ja|宇都宮遯庵}} , a Confucian scholar (born {{ill|1633|ja|1633rd year}} ). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1719|ja|1719th year}} {{ill|November 21|ja|11月21日}} ) – {{ill|Yamamoto Tsuna|ja|山本常朝}} , a {{ill|samurai|ja|Samurai}} (born {{ill|1659|ja|1659th year}} ). * {{ill|Enkyō|ja|Enkyō}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1747|ja|1747th year}} {{ill|November 12|ja|11月12日}} ) – {{ill|Shimazu Yoshitaka|ja|島津吉貴}} , the 4th lord of the {{i