{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=十月初十|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 10월 10일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar October|qq=}} '''October 10''' is the 10th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=}} the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Eiroku|ja|永禄|qq=}} 10th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1567|ja|1567th year|qq=}} {{ill|November 10|ja|11月10日|qq=}} ) – In the {{ill|Todai-ji Daibutsuden Battle|ja|東大寺大仏殿の戦い|qq=}} , due to a surprise attack by {{ill|Matsunaga Hisahide|ja|松永久秀|qq=}} , the {{ill|Todai-ji Daibutsuden|ja|東大寺大仏殿|qq=}} burned down. * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=}} 5th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1577|ja|1577th year|qq=}} {{ill|November 19|ja|11月19日|qq=}} ) – In the {{ill|Shigisan Castle Battle|ja|信貴山城の戦い|qq=}} , {{ill|Matsunaga Hisahide|ja|松永久秀|qq=}} shattered the famed weapon {{ill|Kotenyō Heipingumo|ja|古天明平蜘蛛|qq=}} and subsequently committed suicide. * {{ill|Kanei|ja|寛永|qq=}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1629|ja|1629th year|qq=}} {{ill|November 24|ja|11月24日|qq=}} ) – Fuku, the wet nurse of {{ill|Tokugawa Iemitsu|ja|徳川家光|qq=}} , entered the palace and received the title of {{ill|Kasuga no Tsubone|ja|春日局|qq=}} .
== Births == * {{ill|Genpō|ja|元豊 (宋)|qq=}} 5th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1082|ja|1082nd year|qq=}} {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Huizong|ja|徽宗|qq=}} , the 8th emperor of the {{ill|Northern Song|ja|北宋|qq=}} (died {{ill|1135|ja|1135th year|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Kenpo|ja|建保|qq=}} 6th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1218|ja|1218th year|qq=}} {{ill|October 30|ja|10月30日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Chūkō|ja|仲恭天皇|qq=}} , the 85th {{ill|Emperor|ja|天皇|qq=}} (died {{ill|1234|ja|1234th year|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1830|ja|1830th year|qq=}} {{ill|November 24|ja|11月24日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Seikawa Hachirō|ja|清河八郎|qq=}} , founder of the Mibu rōshitai (the precursor to the {{ill|Shinsengumi|ja|新選組|qq=}} ) (died {{ill|1863|ja|1863rd year|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Dōkō|ja|道光|qq=}} 15th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1835|ja|1835th year|qq=}} {{ill|November 29|ja|11月29日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Empress Dowager Cixi|ja|慈禧太后|qq=}} (Western Empress Dowager), consort of {{ill|Emperor Xianfeng|ja|咸豊帝|qq=}} and a de facto dictator of the late {{ill|Qing Dynasty|ja|清|qq=}} (died {{ill|1908|ja|1908th year|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=}} 13th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1842|ja|1842nd year|qq=}} {{ill|November 12|ja|11月12日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Ōyama Gen|ja|大山厳|qq=}} , Marshal of the Army (died {{ill|1916|ja|1916th year|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Hakuchi|ja|白雉|qq=}} 5th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|654|ja|654th year|qq=}} {{ill|November 24|ja|11月24日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Kōtoku|ja|孝徳天皇|qq=}} , the 36th Emperor. * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1577|ja|1577th year|qq=}} {{ill|November 19|ja|11月19日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Matsunaga Hisahide|ja|松永久秀|qq=}} , a {{ill|samurai|ja|Samurai|qq=}} (born {{ill|1510|ja|1510th year|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1707|ja|1707th year|qq=}} {{ill|November 3|ja|11月3日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Utsunomiya Tonan|ja|宇都宮遯庵|qq=}} , a Confucian scholar (born {{ill|1633|ja|1633rd year|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1719|ja|1719th year|qq=}} {{ill|November 21|ja|11月21日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Yamamoto Tsuna|ja|山本常朝|qq=}} , a {{ill|samurai|ja|Samurai|qq=}} (born {{ill|1659|ja|1659th year|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Enkyō|ja|Enkyō|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1747|ja