* {{ill|Eiroku|ja|永禄|qq=|12=draft}}  10th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1567|ja|1567th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 10|ja|11月10日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – In the {{ill|Todai-ji Daibutsuden Battle|ja|東大寺大仏殿の戦い|qq=|12=draft}} , due to a surprise attack by {{ill|Matsunaga Hisahide|ja|松永久秀|qq=|12=draft}} , the {{ill|Todai-ji Daibutsuden|ja|東大寺大仏殿|qq=|12=draft}}  burned down.
* {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|12=draft}}  5th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1577|ja|1577th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 19|ja|11月19日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – In the {{ill|Shigisan Castle Battle|ja|信貴山城の戦い|qq=|12=draft}} , {{ill|Matsunaga Hisahide|ja|松永久秀|qq=|12=draft}}  shattered the famed weapon {{ill|Kotenyō Heipingumo|ja|古天明平蜘蛛|qq=|12=draft}}  and subsequently committed suicide.
* {{ill|Kanei|ja|寛永|qq=|12=draft}}  6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1629|ja|1629th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 24|ja|11月24日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – Fuku, the wet nurse of {{ill|Tokugawa Iemitsu|ja|徳川家光|qq=|12=draft}} , entered the palace and received the title of {{ill|Kasuga no Tsubone|ja|春日局|qq=|12=draft}} .

