'''October 10''' is the 10th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} . 

== Events ==
* {{ill|Eiroku|ja|永禄|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  10th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1567|ja|1567th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 10|ja|11月10日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – In the {{ill|Todai-ji Daibutsuden Battle|ja|東大寺大仏殿の戦い|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , due to a surprise attack by {{ill|Matsunaga Hisahide|ja|松永久秀|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , the {{ill|Todai-ji Daibutsuden|ja|東大寺大仏殿|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  burned down.
* {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  5th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1577|ja|1577th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 19|ja|11月19日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – In the {{ill|Shigisan Castle Battle|ja|信貴山城の戦い|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Matsunaga Hisahide|ja|松永久秀|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  shattered the famed weapon {{ill|Kotenyō Heipingumo|ja|古天明平蜘蛛|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  and subsequently committed suicide.
* {{ill|Kanei|ja|寛永|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1629|ja|1629th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 24|ja|11月24日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – Fuku, the wet nurse of {{ill|Tokugawa Iemitsu|ja|徳川家光|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , entered the palace and received the title of {{ill|Kasuga no Tsubone|ja|春日局|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} .

== Births ==
* {{ill|Genpō|ja|元豊 (宋)|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  5th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1082|ja|1082nd year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Huizong|ja|徽宗|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 8th emperor of the {{ill|Northern Song|ja|北宋|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  (died {{ill|1135|ja|1135th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Kenpo|ja|建保|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  6th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1218|ja|1218th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 30|ja|10月30日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Chūkō|ja|仲恭天皇|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 85th {{ill|Emperor|ja|天皇|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  (died {{ill|1234|ja|1234th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1830|ja|1830th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 24|ja|11月24日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Seikawa Hachirō|ja|清河八郎|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , founder of the Mibu rōshitai (the precursor to the {{ill|Shinsengumi|ja|新選組|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ) (died {{ill|1863|ja|1863rd year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Dōkō|ja|道光|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  15th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1835|ja|1835th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 29|ja|11月29日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Empress Dowager Cixi|ja|慈禧太后|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  (Western Empress Dowager), consort of {{ill|Emperor Xianfeng|ja|咸豊帝|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  and a de facto dictator of the late {{ill|Qing Dynasty|ja|清|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  (died {{ill|1908|ja|1908th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  13th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1842|ja|1842nd year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 12|ja|11月12日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Ōyama Gen|ja|大山厳|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , Marshal of the Army (died {{ill|1916|ja|1916th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ).

