== Events == * {{ill|Eiroku|ja|永禄|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Eiroku|qq=}} 10th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1567|ja|1567年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1567|qq=}} {{ill|November 10|ja|11月10日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 10|qq=}} ) – In the {{ill|Todai-ji Daibutsuden Battle|ja|東大寺大仏殿の戦い|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Todai-ji Daibutsuden Battle|qq=}} , due to a surprise attack by {{ill|Matsunaga Hisahide|ja|松永久秀|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Matsunaga Hisahide|qq=}} , the {{ill|Todai-ji Daibutsuden|ja|東大寺大仏殿|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Todai-ji Daibutsuden|qq=}} burned down. * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō (Momoyama period)|qq=}} 5th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1577|ja|1577年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1577|qq=}} {{ill|November 19|ja|11月19日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 19|qq=}} ) – In the {{ill|Shigisan Castle Battle|ja|信貴山城の戦い|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shigisan Castle Battle|qq=}} , {{ill|Matsunaga Hisahide|ja|松永久秀|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Matsunaga Hisahide|qq=}} shattered the famed weapon {{ill|Kotenyō Heipingumo|ja|古天明平蜘蛛|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kotenyō Heipingumo|qq=}} and subsequently committed suicide. * {{ill|Kanei|ja|寛永|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanei|qq=}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1629|ja|1629年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1629|qq=}} {{ill|November 24|ja|11月24日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 24|qq=}} ) – Fuku, the wet nurse of {{ill|Tokugawa Iemitsu|ja|徳川家光|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Iemitsu|qq=}} , entered the palace and received the title of {{ill|Kasuga no Tsubone|ja|春日局|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kasuga no Tsubone|qq=}} .
== Births == * {{ill|Genpō|ja|元豊 (宋)|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genpō|qq=}} 5th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1082|ja|1082nd year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1082|qq=}} {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 2|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Huizong|ja|徽宗|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Huizong|qq=}} , the 8th emperor of the {{ill|Northern Song|ja|北宋|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Northern Song|qq=}} (died {{ill|1135|ja|1135年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1135|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Kenpo|ja|建保|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kenpo|qq=}} 6th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1218|ja|1218年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1218|qq=}} {{ill|October 30|ja|10月30日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 30|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Chūkō|ja|仲恭天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Chūkō|qq=}} , the 85th {{ill|Emperor|ja|天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor|qq=}} (died {{ill|1234|ja|1234年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1234|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1830|ja|1830年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1830|qq=}} {{ill|November 24|ja|11月24日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 24|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Seikawa Hachirō|ja|清河八郎|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Seikawa Hachirō|qq=}} , founder of the Mibu rōshitai (the precursor to the {{ill|Shinsengumi|ja|新選組|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shinsengumi|qq=}} ) (died {{ill|1863|ja|1863年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1863|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Dōkō|ja|道光|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Dōkō|qq=}} 15th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1835|ja|1835年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1835|qq=}} {{ill|November 29|ja|11月29日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 29|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Empress Dowager Cixi|ja|慈禧太后|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Empress Dowager Cixi|qq=}} (Western Empress Dowager), consort of {{ill|Emperor Xianfeng|ja|咸豊帝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Xianfeng|qq=}} and a de facto dictator of the late {{ill|Qing Dynasty|ja|清|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Qing Dynasty|qq=}} (died {{ill|1908|ja|1908年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1908|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō|qq=}} 13th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1842|ja|1842nd year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1842|qq=}} {{ill|November 12|ja|11月12日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 12|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Ōyama Gen|ja|大山厳|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōyama Gen|qq=}} , Marshal of the Army (died {{ill|1916|ja|1916年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1916|qq=}} ).
