le/Tenpō|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1830|ja|1830年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1830|qq=}} {{ill|November 24|ja|11月24日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 24|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Seikawa Hachirō|ja|清河八郎|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Seikawa Hachirō|qq=}} , founder of the Mibu rōshitai (the precursor to the {{ill|Shinsengumi|ja|新選組|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shinsengumi|qq=}} ) (died {{ill|1863|ja|1863年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1863|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Dōkō|ja|道光|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Dōkō|qq=}} 15th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1835|ja|1835年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1835|qq=}} {{ill|November 29|ja|11月29日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 29|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Empress Dowager Cixi|ja|慈禧太后|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Empress Dowager Cixi|qq=}} (Western Empress Dowager), consort of {{ill|Emperor Xianfeng|ja|咸豊帝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Xianfeng|qq=}} and a de facto dictator of the late {{ill|Qing Dynasty|ja|清|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Qing Dynasty|qq=}} (died {{ill|1908|ja|1908年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1908|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō|qq=}}