== Events == * [[:en:Eiroku|Eiroku]] 10th year ( [[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1567|1567]] [[:en:November 10|November 10]] ) – In the {{ill|Todai-ji Daibutsuden Battle|ja|東大寺大仏殿の戦い|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Todai-ji Daibutsuden Battle|qq=}} , due to a surprise attack by [[:en:Matsunaga Hisahide|Matsunaga Hisahide]] , the {{ill|Todai-ji Daibutsuden|ja|東大寺大仏殿|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Todai-ji Daibutsuden|qq=}} burned down. * [[:en:Tenshō (Momoyama period)|Tenshō Era]] 5th year ( [[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1577|1577]] [[:en:November 19|November 19]] ) – In the [[:en:Siege of Shigisan|Shigisan Castle Battle]] , [[:en:Matsunaga Hisahide|Matsunaga Hisahide]] shattered the famed weapon {{ill|Kotenyō Heipingumo|ja|古天明平蜘蛛|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kotenyō Heipingumo|qq=}} and subsequently committed suicide. * [[:en:Kan'ei|Kanei]] 6th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1629|1629]] [[:en:November 24|November 24]] ) – Fuku, the wet nurse of [[:en:Tokugawa Iemitsu|Tokugawa Iemitsu]] , entered the palace and received the title of [[:en:Lady Kasuga|Kasuga no Tsubone]] .
== Births == * {{ill|Genpō|ja|元豊 (宋)|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genpō|qq=}} 5th year ( [[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1082|1082]] [[:en:November 2|November 2]] ) – [[:en:Emperor Huizong of Song|Huizong]] , the 8th emperor of the {{ill|Northern Song|ja|北宋|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Northern Song|qq=}} (died [[:en:1135|1135]] ). * [[:en:Kempo (era)|Kenpo]] 6th year ( [[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1218|1218]] [[:en:October 30|October 30]] ) – [[:en:Emperor Chūkyō|Emperor Chūkō]] , the 85th [[:en:Emperor of Japan|Emperor]] (died [[:en:1234|1234]] ). * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 1st year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1830|1830]] [[:en:November 24|November 24]] ) – {{ill|Seikawa Hachirō|ja|清河八郎|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Seikawa Hachirō|qq=}} , founder of the Mibu rōshitai (the precursor to the [[:en:Shinsengumi|Shinsengumi]] ) (died [[:en:1863|1863]] ). * {{ill|Dōkō|ja|道光|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Dōkō|qq=}} 15th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1835|1835]] [[:en:November 29|November 29]] ) – {{ill|Empress Dowager Cixi|ja|慈禧太后|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Empress Dowager Cixi|qq=}} (Western Empress Dowager), consort of [[:en:Xianfeng Emperor|Emperor Xianfeng]] and a de facto dictator of the late [[:en:Qing dynasty|Qing Dynasty]] (died [[:en:1908|1908]] ). * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 13th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1842|1842]] [[:en:November 12|November 12]] ) – {{ill|Ōyama Gen|ja|大山厳|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōyama Gen|qq=}} , Marshal of the Army (died [[:en:1916|1916]] ).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Hakuchi (era)|Hakuchi]] 5th year ( [[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:654|654]] [[:en:November 24|November 24]] ) – [[:en:Emperor Kōtoku|Emperor Kōtoku]] , the 36th Emperor. * [[:en:Tenshō (Momoyama period)|Tenshō Era]] 5th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1577|1577]] [[:en:November 19|November 19]] ) – [[:en:Matsunaga Hisahide|Matsunaga Hisahide]] , a {{ill|samurai|ja|Samurai|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/samurai|qq=}} (born [[:en:1510|1510]] ). * [[:en:Hōei|Hōei]] 4th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1707|1707]] [[:en:November 3|November 3]] ) – {{ill|Utsunomiya Tonan|ja|宇都宮遯庵|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Utsunomiya Tonan|qq=}} , a Confucian scholar (born [[:en:1633|1633]] ). * [[:en:Kyōhō|Kyōhō]] 4th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1719|1719]] [[:en:November 21|November 21]] ) – [[:en:Yamamoto Tsunetomo|Yamamoto Tsuna]] , a {{ill|samurai|ja|Samurai|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/samurai|qq=}} (born [[:en:1659|1659]] ). * {{ill|Enkyō|ja|Enkyō|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Enkyō|qq=}} 4th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1747|1747]] [[:en:November 12|November 12]] ) – {{ill|Shimazu Yoshitaka|ja|島津吉貴|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shimazu Yoshitaka|qq=}} , the 4th lord of the [[:en:Satsuma Domain|Satsuma Domain]] (born [[:en:1675|1675]] ).
== Commemorations == {{ill|Tokan'ya|ja|十日夜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokan'ya|qq=}} (とおかんや)
