== Events == * {{ill|Eiroku|en|Eiroku|WD=Q1143341|lt=Eiroku|1=Eiroku}} 10th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|WD=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1567|en|1567|WD=Q6642|lt=1567|1=1567}} {{ill|November 10|en|November 10|WD=Q2988|lt=November 10|1=November 10}} ) – In the {{ill|Todai-ji Daibutsuden Battle|ja|東大寺大仏殿の戦い|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Todai-ji Daibutsuden Battle|1=Battle of Tōdai-ji Daibutsuden|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11526465}} , due to a surprise attack by {{ill|Matsunaga Hisahide|en|Matsunaga Hisahide|WD=Q1143038|lt=Matsunaga Hisahide|1=Matsunaga Hisahide}} , the {{ill|Todai-ji Daibutsuden|ja|東大寺大仏殿|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Todai-ji Daibutsuden|1=Great Buddha Hall|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q3012032}} burned down. * {{ill|Tenshō (Momoyama period)|en|Tenshō (Momoyama period)|WD=Q1145058|lt=Tenshō Era|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)}} 5th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|WD=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1577|en|1577|WD=Q6704|lt=1577|1=1577}} {{ill|November 19|en|November 19|WD=Q3026|lt=November 19|1=November 19}} ) – In the {{ill|Siege of Shigisan|en|Siege of Shigisan|WD=Q6132231|lt=Shigisan Castle Battle|1=Siege of Shigisan}} , {{ill|Matsunaga Hisahide|en|Matsunaga Hisahide|WD=Q1143038|lt=Matsunaga Hisahide|1=Matsunaga Hisahide}} shattered the famed weapon {{ill|Kotenyō Heipingumo|ja|古天明平蜘蛛|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kotenyō Heipingumo|1=Kotenmyō Hiragumo|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11411022}} and subsequently committed suicide. * {{ill|Kan'ei|en|Kan'ei|WD=Q1192913|lt=Kanei|1=Kan'ei}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1629|en|1629|WD=Q6847|lt=1629|1=1629}} {{ill|November 24|en|November 24|WD=Q3022|lt=November 24|1=November 24}} ) – Fuku, the wet nurse of {{ill|Tokugawa Iemitsu|en|Tokugawa Iemitsu|WD=Q314481|lt=Tokugawa Iemitsu|1=Tokugawa Iemitsu}} , entered the palace and received the title of {{ill|Lady Kasuga|en|Lady Kasuga|WD=Q835747|lt=Kasuga no Tsubone|1=Lady Kasuga}} .
== Births == * {{ill|Genpō|ja|元豊 (宋)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genpō|1=Yuanfeng|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q10889531}} 5th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|WD=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1082|en|1082|WD=Q19452|lt=1082|1=1082}} {{ill|November 2|en|November 2|WD=Q2996|lt=November 2|1=November 2}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Huizong of Song|en|Emperor Huizong of Song|WD=Q7486|lt=Huizong|1=Emperor Huizong of Song}} , the 8th emperor of the {{ill|Northern Song|ja|北宋|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Northern Song|comment=changed title based on wikidata|1=Northern Song (960–1127)|WD=Q319460}} (died {{ill|1135|en|1135|WD=Q19594|lt=1135|1=1135}} ). * {{ill|Kempo (era)|en|Kempo (era)|WD=Q1194251|lt=Kenpo|1=Kempo (era)}} 6th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|WD=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1218|en|1218|WD=Q5381|lt=1218|1=1218}} {{ill|October 30|en|October 30|WD=Q2950|lt=October 30|1=October 30}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Chūkyō|en|Emperor Chūkyō|WD=Q357253|lt=Emperor Chūkō|1=Emperor Chūkyō}} , the 85th {{ill|Emperor of Japan|en|Emperor of Japan|WD=Q208233|lt=Emperor|1=Emperor of Japan}} (died {{ill|1234|en|1234|WD=Q5424|lt=1234|1=1234}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|en|Tenpō|WD=Q1369045|lt=Tenpō|1=Tenpō}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1830|en|1830|WD=Q7576|lt=1830|1=1830}} {{ill|November 24|en|November 24|WD=Q3022|lt=November 24|1=November 24}} ) – {{ill|Seikawa Hachirō|ja|清河八郎|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Seikawa Hachirō|1=Kiyokawa Hachirō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q129812}} , founder of the Mibu rōshitai (the precursor to the {{ill|Shinsengumi|en|Shinsengumi|WD=Q221031|lt=Shinsengumi|1=Shinsengumi}} ) (died {{ill|1863|en|1863|WD=Q7701|lt=1863|1=1863}} ). * {{ill|Dōkō|ja|道光|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Dōkō|1=Daoguang Era|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q1133186}} 15th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1835|en|1835|WD=Q7597|lt=1835|1=1835}} {{ill|November 29|en|November 29|WD=Q3016|lt=November 29|1=November 29}} ) – {{ill|Empress Dowager Cixi|ja|慈禧太后|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Empress Dowager Cixi|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 西太后|1=Empress Dowager Cixi|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q47842}} (Western Empress Dowager), consort of {{ill|Xianfeng Emperor|en|Xianfeng Emperor|WD=Q334452|lt=Emperor Xianfeng|1=Xianfeng Emperor}} and a de facto dictator of the late {{ill|Qing dynasty|en|Qing dynasty|WD=Q8733|lt=Qing Dynasty|1=Qing dynasty}} (died {{ill|1908|en|1908|WD=Q2056|lt=1908|1=1908}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|en|Tenpō|WD=Q1369045|lt=Tenpō|1=Tenpō}} 13th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1842|en|1842|WD=Q7625|lt=1842|1=1842}} {{ill|November 12|en|November 12|WD=Q2986|lt=November 12|1=November 12}} ) – {{ill|Ōyama Gen|ja|大山厳|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōyama Gen|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 大山巌|1=Ōyama Iwao|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q359819}} , Marshal of the Army (died {{ill|1916|en|1916|WD=Q2087|lt=1916|1=1916}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Hakuchi (era)|en|Hakuchi (era)|WD=Q540118|lt=Hakuchi|1=Hakuchi (era)}} 5th year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|WD=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|654|en|654|WD=Q31109|lt=654|1=654}} {{ill|November 24|en|November 24|WD=Q3022|lt=November 24|1=November 24}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Kōtoku|en|Emperor Kōtoku|WD=Q317980|lt=Emperor Kōtoku|1=Emperor Kōtoku}} , the 36th Emperor. * {{ill|Tenshō (Momoyama period)|en|Tenshō (Momoyama period)|WD=Q1145058|lt=Tenshō Era|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1577|en|1577|WD=Q6704|lt=1577|1=1577}} {{ill|November 19|en|November 19|WD=Q3026|lt=November 19|1=November 19}} ) – {{ill|Matsunaga Hisahide|en|Matsunaga Hisahide|WD=Q1143038|lt=Matsunaga Hisahide|1=Matsunaga Hisahide}} , a {{ill|samurai|ja|Samurai|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/samurai|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to サムライ|1=Samurai (disambiguation)|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q529624}} (born {{ill|1510|en|1510|WD=Q6182|lt=1510|1=1510}} ). * {{ill|Hōei|en|Hōei|WD=Q1145262|lt=Hōei|1=Hōei}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1707|en|1707|WD=Q6841|lt=1707|1=1707}} {{ill|November 3|en|November 3|WD=Q2995|lt=November 3|1=November 3}} ) – {{ill|Utsunomiya Tonan|ja|宇都宮遯庵|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Utsunomiya Tonan|1=Utsunomiya Ton'an|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q6561283}} , a Confucian scholar (born {{ill|1633|en|1633|WD=Q6870|lt=1633|1=1633}} ). * {{ill|Kyōhō|en|Kyōhō|WD=Q1145048|lt=Kyōhō|1=Kyōhō}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1719|en|1719|WD=Q6902|lt=1719|1=1719}} {{ill|November 21|en|November 21|WD=Q3023|lt=November 21|1=November 21}} ) – {{ill|Yamamoto Tsunetomo|en|Yamamoto Tsunetomo|WD=Q548162|lt=Yamamoto Tsuna|1=Yamamoto Tsunetomo}} , a {{ill|samurai|ja|Samurai|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/samurai|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to サムライ|1=Samurai (disambiguation)|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q529624}} (born {{ill|1659|en|1659|WD=Q6995|lt=1659|1=1659}} ). * {{ill|Enkyō|1=Enkyō (Edo period)|2=ja|3=延享|lt=Enkyō|ja|Enkyō|1=Enkyō (Edo period)|2=ja|3=延享|lt=Enkyō|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Enkyō|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q1183728}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1747|en|1747|WD=Q7596|lt=1747|1=1747}} {{ill|November 12|en|November 12|WD=Q2986|lt=November 12|1=November 12}} ) – {{ill|Shimazu Yoshitaka|ja|島津吉貴|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shimazu Yoshitaka|1=Shimazu Yoshitaka|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11246537}} , the 4th lord of the {{ill|Satsuma Domain|en|Satsuma Domain|WD=Q676187|lt=Satsuma Domain|1=Satsuma Domain}} (born {{ill|1675|en|1675|WD=Q7624|lt=1675|1=1675}} ).
